description.plain:
Maren Morris is a country singer and songwriter. Like many country artists, she works in Nashville, TN.

Her debut album Hero performed well after the single “My Church” went viral, prompting many to herald her as the future of country music.

songs.title: My Church

description.plain:
In this song, Maren Morris uses traditionally religious rhetoric to communicate the depth of her feelings about music and songwriting.

In an interview with Genius, Morris described it as “a road song.”

I wrote it in a place of inspiration. I get a lot of my songwriting done while driving around Nashville—sometimes it comes to me that way. I tried to write about that feeling, that connection.

https://twitter.com/MarenMorris/status/575786590582087680

songs.title: Rich

description.plain: “Rich” is a hit Country Pop song that gained lots of popularity in Late 2018 and Early 2019, Rich is also the 2nd song in Maren Morris' hit debut album “HERO”, it got very popular and later she preformed on the 2018 ACM and a Platinum by the RIAA.
